      • validateField

        public static String validateField(@Nullable
                                   String text,
                                   int size)
        Checks if a field consists of the minimum number of characters. If it contains fewer characters than required, a warning text is appended to the field text, padding it until it exceeds the minimum required size.
        Parameters:
        text - field text
        size - minimum field size (in number of characters)
        Returns:
        validated field meeting the minimum required length, or the original null or empty string
